Description
Appointment
Class for appointment objects that will populate appointment table view in directory.
CreateApptController
Controller for create-appt-view allows the user to generate appointments.

Controller class for the create-customer-view that allows user to add customer to database.
Customer
Class for creating customer objects that will be used to populate customer table view.
DirectoryController
Controller class for the directory-view.fxml that shows all customers and user appointments in table views, allows the user to add or edit them, and allows the user to generate reports.

Controller for the edit-appt-view populates fields with selected appointment information and allows user to edit appointment.

Controller for the edit-customer-view that allows user to edit selected customer information.

LoginController
Class that allows the user to log in to the scheduler app, establishes a database connection, and generates a history of login attempts.

Abstract class that logs login attempt information to a text file
